  <entry>
    <title>2024-02-01 CS50-Week7-SQl</title>
    <link href="/2024/02/01/CS50-Week7-SQl/"/>
    <url>/2024/02/01/CS50-Week7-SQl/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>第一篇学习记录，比起写什么怎么写更让人纠结<br>目前计划大概是根据<a href="https://csdiy.wiki/">csdiy</a>的学习规划进行，CS50过后大概是CS61A,在四月入学前与mit的微积分线性代数一并完成（？）,试一下markdown</p><ul><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <a href="https://cs50.harvard.edu/x/2024/">CS50(Week7)</a></li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <a href="https://cs61a.org/">CS61A(新建文件夹)</a></li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <a href="https://ocw.mit.edu/courses/18-01sc-single-variable-calculus-fall-2010/pages/syllabus/">MIT18.01(新建文件夹)</a>,<a href="https://ocw.mit.edu/courses/18-02sc-multivariable-calculus-fall-2010/">MIT18.02(新建文件夹)</a></li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <a href="https://ocw.mit.edu/courses/18-06sc-linear-algebra-fall-2011/pages/syllabus/">MIT18.06(新建文件夹)</a><br>不知道该说是太能拖了还是太鶸了,预计学时20小时的课程从去年十二月到现在一个月了还是停滞在sql…<br>趁现在blog也搭好了趁机再开吧。<br>由于时间不够看完lecture于是选择了时间更短的section。</li></ul><h1 id="Section"><a href="#Section" class="headerlink" title="Section"></a>Section</h1><h2 id="private-key-foreign-key"><a href="#private-key-foreign-key" class="headerlink" title="private key,foreign key"></a>private key,foreign key</h2><ol><li>a primary key is thay unique id for every row in that table.当primary key在其他table被使用时即foreign key。</li><li>多对多关系时常用joined table或说junction table来表示table之间的关系</li></ol><h2 id="Design-principles"><a href="#Design-principles" class="headerlink" title="Design principles"></a>Design principles</h2><ul><li>Create one table for each entity in your dataset</li><li>All tablese should have a primary key.</li><li>The information in that table should depend on the primary key only.</li></ul><h3 id="Create-a-new-database-file-called-read-db"><a href="#Create-a-new-database-file-called-read-db" class="headerlink" title="Create a new database file called read.db"></a>Create a new database file called read.db</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ sqlite3 reads.db<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>应该会变成这样:</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="SQL-syntax"><a href="#SQL-syntax" class="headerlink" title="SQL syntax"></a>SQL syntax</h2><h3 id="Create-table-types’-kinds"><a href="#Create-table-types’-kinds" class="headerlink" title="Create table,types’ kinds"></a>Create table,types’ kinds</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">CREATE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">TABLE</span> table_name (<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>column0 <span class="hljs-type">INTEGER</span>,<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>column1 TEXT,<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>column2 <span class="hljs-type">NUMERIC</span>,<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>column3 <span class="hljs-type">REAL</span><br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> );<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Set-primary-key"><a href="#Set-primary-key" class="headerlink" title="Set primary key"></a>Set primary key</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">CREATE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">TABLE</span> table_name (<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>column0 <span class="hljs-type">INTEGER</span>,<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>column1 TEXT,<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>column2 <span class="hljs-type">NUMERIC</span>,<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>column3 <span class="hljs-type">REAL</span>,<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span><span class="hljs-keyword">PRIMARY</span> KEY(column0)<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> );<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Tell-me-what-tables-do-i-have-in-this-database"><a href="#Tell-me-what-tables-do-i-have-in-this-database" class="headerlink" title="Tell me what tables do i have in this database"></a>Tell me what tables do i have in this database</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> .tables<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="what-the-columns-is-in-the-table"><a href="#what-the-columns-is-in-the-table" class="headerlink" title="what the columns is in the table"></a>what the columns is in the table</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> .schema <span class="hljs-keyword">table</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="joined-table的primary-key？"><a href="#joined-table的primary-key？" class="headerlink" title="joined table的primary key？"></a>joined table的primary key？</h2><p>authored table里面有author id和book id两个column，似乎这俩个哪一个都不是authored table的primary id？</p><p>authored table的primary key并非单独哪一个column，而是这两个column的组合作为该table的primary id</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">CREATE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">TABLE</span> authored (<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>    author_id <span class="hljs-type">INTEGER</span>,<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>    book_id <span class="hljs-type">INTEGER</span>,<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">PRIMARY</span> KEY(author_id,book_id),<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>    FOREGIN KEY(author_id) <span class="hljs-keyword">REFERENCES</span> author(id),<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>    FOREGIN KEY(book_id) <span class="hljs-keyword">REFERENCES</span> booke(id)<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> );<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Inserting-Deleting"><a href="#Inserting-Deleting" class="headerlink" title="Inserting,Deleting"></a>Inserting,Deleting</h2><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">INSERT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">INTO</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">table</span> (column0,column1)<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">VALUES</span>(value0,value1);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">DELETE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">table</span><br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">WHERE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">condition</span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Example"><a href="#Example" class="headerlink" title="Example"></a>Example</h3><p><em>Inserting</em></p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">INSERT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">INTO</span> books (tittle,pubished,rating)<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">VALUES</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Flights&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;2017-05-17&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-number">4</span>);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>尽管并没有输入作为books table的primary key，id</strong><br><strong>但实际上primary key会被自动添加</strong><br><em>一次添加多个值</em><br>将<code>...&gt;    VALUES(&#39;Flights&#39;,&#39;2017-05-17&#39;,4);</code>中的<code>;</code>更改为<code>,</code>并继续重复直到停止添加以<code>;</code>结尾即可</p><p><em>Selecting</em></p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="hljs-operator">*</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> books;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>Delecting</em></p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">DELETE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> books;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>TIPS:这会直接删除整个book table</em></p><p>想删除个别时使用WHERE … &#x3D; …</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">DELETE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> books <span class="hljs-keyword">WHERE</span> tittle <span class="hljs-operator">=</span><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Flights&#x27;</span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Leave-sqlite"><a href="#Leave-sqlite" class="headerlink" title="Leave sqlite"></a>Leave sqlite</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> .quit<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="read-doc"><a href="#read-doc" class="headerlink" title="read doc"></a>read doc</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> .read <span class="hljs-number">1.</span><span class="hljs-keyword">sql</span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>read into sqlite,runing and sql statements it sees</em></p><p><strong>SELECT</strong><br><strong>WHERE</strong><br><strong>LIKE</strong><br><strong>ORDER BY</strong></p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs SQL">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> name <br>sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> songs<br>sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">ORDER</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">BY</span> duration<span class="hljs-operator">-</span>ms <span class="hljs-keyword">DESC</span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>ASC:ascending,升序</strong><br><strong>DESC:descending,降序</strong></p><h2 id="Aggregate-Function"><a href="#Aggregate-Function" class="headerlink" title="Aggregate Function"></a>Aggregate Function</h2><h3 id="Keywords-to-calculate-data-from-multiple"><a href="#Keywords-to-calculate-data-from-multiple" class="headerlink" title="Keywords to calculate data from multiple"></a>Keywords to calculate data from multiple</h3><p><strong>SELECT COUNT</strong>(column)<br><strong>FORM</strong> table<br><strong>WHERE</strong> condition;</p><p><strong>SELECT AVG</strong>(column)<br><strong>FROM</strong> table<br><strong>WHERE</strong> condition;</p><p><strong>SELECT ROUND(AVG(energy)，2)</strong></p><h2 id="Combining-Tables"><a href="#Combining-Tables" class="headerlink" title="Combining Tables"></a>Combining Tables</h2><h3 id="Methods-to-reference-data-from-multiple-tables"><a href="#Methods-to-reference-data-from-multiple-tables" class="headerlink" title="Methods to reference data from multiple tables"></a>Methods to reference data from multiple tables</h3><p><strong>Sub queries</strong><br><strong>Join</strong></p><p><strong>Sub queries</strong></p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> rating<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> ratings<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">WHERE</span> movie_id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> (<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> id<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> movies<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">WHERE</span> tittle <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Cars 3&#x27;</span><br>    );<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>join</strong></p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> songs.name,energy,artists.name<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> songs<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">JOIN</span> artists <span class="hljs-keyword">ON</span> artists.id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> songs.artists_id<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">WHERE</span> artists.name <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Drake&#x27;</span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Like"><a href="#Like" class="headerlink" title="Like"></a>Like</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> name<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> songs<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">WHERE</span> name <span class="hljs-keyword">LIKE</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;%feat.%&#x27;</span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Group-by"><a href="#Group-by" class="headerlink" title="Group by"></a>Group by</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql">sqlite<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> atrists.name, <span class="hljs-built_in">COUNT</span>(artists.name)<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> songs<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">JOIN</span> artists <span class="hljs-keyword">ON</span> atrists,id <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> songs.artist_id<br>...<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">GROUP</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">BY</span> artists.name;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
